{
  "description": "A wide-angle shot presents a view of San Francisco, prominently featuring the Bay Bridge stretching across a vibrant blue body of water. The bridge is a massive steel structure with prominent towers and suspension cables. Behind it, the city skyline rises, composed of numerous buildings of varying heights. A mix of high-rise apartments and older, shorter buildings create a diverse urban landscape. A green hill is visible in the background, adding a natural element to the scene. Several boats and ships are dotted on the water near the waterfront, and a construction crane is visible among the buildings. The water's surface exhibits subtle wave patterns, reflecting the bright daylight.",
